title: Multilingual Poetry Collection 002
creator: Various
description:
In LibriVox's Multilingual Poetry Collection, LibriVox volunteers read their favourite public-domain poems in languages other than English.
The LibriVox catalog page for this work lists the authors and the LibriVox readers, and has links to the texts. For more information on LibriVox, or to volunteer, please see:http://librivox.org/
